                                            Let's hope they finish this one.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The Free Software Foundation (FSF) is starting a new project called LibrePhone. Announced during the FSF's 40th birthday celebration earlier this month, this initiative is to build a mobile platform starting right from the firmware all the way up to the operating system.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 08 Oct 2025 17:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/the-free-software-foundation-is-making-an-open-source-phone/</guid></item></channel>
